**Example 1: RemoveWorkspace**



Input: 

```
tccli cloudstudio RemoveWorkspace --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --Force true \
    --CloudStudioSessionTeam cloudstudio-devops \
    --SpaceKey iqybry
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "RequestId": "dd62f2ad-9fd4-41f7-9cdb-b98cece5d879"
    }
}
```
